        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nHi Claudio,\n\nIt is interesting to see the Google Cache library in action\nAs indicated by the acceptance criteria it is the SchemaContext (Yang Tools produced class) we need to cache! I suppose it wil be easy to change to that.\nThe only question really is what class will be responsible for creating and caching the Schemacontext objects. I would suggest the CpsModuleService (non-public API)",
