        "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nNot sure if I missed the grooming for this. In general, i would like to discuss the idea of having a cache as a separate and optional component, like we have the DB choice open. A vendor may like to plugin an existing cache(Redis etc) or have his own implementation for it. The DB choice could in some ways influence this too. We could def have a reference impl, but seems we should discuss this more.",
